import { Component } from '@angular/core'; import { Router } from '@angular/router'; import { Usuario } from './shared'; import { LoginService } from './auth/services/login.service'; @Component({ selector: 'app-root', templateUrl: './app.component.html', styleUrls: ['./app.component.css'] }) export class AppComponent { title = 'Trabalho Equipe 3'; constructor( private router: Router, private loginService: LoginService, ) { } get usuarioLogado(): Usuario | null { return this.loginService.usuarioLogado; } logout() { this.loginService.logout(); this.router.navigate(['/login']); } }
